data.description: Lakefront property with no HOA?! Come check out this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located on the skiable Bass Lake! Off the entry you’ll find a guest bedroom with built in shelving that would make for the perfect work from home space. Down the hallway are the remaining 2 bedrooms plus a full bathroom. At the heart of the home you’ll find the open concept living, dining room, and kitchen. This immaculate kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The back wall of the home provides the best views around with direct lake views to wake up to each day! The primary bedroom tucked up at the back offers French doors leading out back, a walk-in closet, and beautiful en-suite with soaking tub and glass front shower. The laundry room creates easy access from the kitchen or through the primary bedroom closet. Out back is the perfect tropical oasis to escape to after a long day! The screened in porch is the place to relax while looking out over the lakes spectacular sunsets! Sitting on over an acre this home checks off all the boxes and more for your growing family! Schedule your private showing today, you won’t want to miss out on the opportunity to call this place “home”!
